    ItemPosition
    This class represents the named position of a point in XYZ plane.
    ObstacleList
    The obstacle list is defined here It contains methods that are useful for path planning
    Obstacles
    The obstacle is defined here Each obstacle is a polygon, the list of points should construct a closed shape
    PIDController
    A PID (proportional-integral-derivative) controller implementation, with additional modifications of saturation limit, wind-up limit, output slope limit, stored setpoint, and lowpass filtering of the derivative signal.
    PIDParams
    A small, plain-old-data helper class to initialize PIDController instances.
    Point3i
    This class represents an immutable point in XYZ plane.

    TraceWriter maintains an XML and provides a simple interface for writing system events and variables.
    Vector3f

    Vector3i

Package edu.illinois.mitra.starl.objects Description

Objects used for assorted purposes. This includes general helper functions, Point and Vector classes, PID-related objects, and Obstacles.
